semsim.annotation

Class SemSimTermLibrary

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.Observable
      • semsim.annotation.SemSimTermLibrary

  • public class SemSimTermLibrary
extends java.util.Observable
    This class is the central repository for all SemSim annotations in an annotator tab. Each annotation is wrapped in an instance of the IndexCard class which is stored in a single ordered list (masterlist). The indicies of each instance of a particular SemSim type are stored in seperate ArrayLists. Durring run time, items in the masterlist are not removed. Instead, its index is removed from its corresponding type index list and it's flagged as deleted.
    Author:
    Christopher
